SENATE CHAMBER
STATE OF OKLAHOMA DISPOSITION
FLOOR AMENDMENT No. ________
COMMITTEE AMENDMENT
(Date)
I move to amend House Bill No. 3413 on Page 4, Line 9, by inserting after the word “contract” and
before the period, the following language: “. Agencies that maintain and publish contract data on
their own website that substantially conforms to the requirements of this act may submit a request to
the Office of Management and Enterprise Services for approval to satisfy the posting requirements
by providing a hyperlink to such data. The Office of Management and Enterprise Services shall
approve the request upon determining that the agency’s website provides information that is
substantially similar in content, format, and accessibility to the requirements of this act. Upon
approval, the Office of Management and Enterprise Services shall include and maintain the
hyperlink in the same location as other agency contract data collected pursuant to this act”.
Submitted by:
